Package: libtabularasa-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: libtabularasa0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Slim C++ library for generating printable tables
 A slim C++ library which can be used to generate formatted tables
 which can be printed using monospace fonts. The borders are only using
 standard characters (-, |, +).
 .
 This package contains the development files.

